The tutorial popped up multiple times in the middle of a project, and erased the edits I was working on. This is a poor design.  The ads are super frequen...Full ReviewOverall, this app is ok.  The features and tools are good. I like the meme creator in particular.  The app isn't without it's shortfalls though.  The tutorial popped up multiple times in the middle of a project, and erased the edits I was working on. This is a poor design.  The ads are super frequent and very annoying. I understand the need for ads to keep the app free, but it was irritating to the point I rarely use this app anymore.

HOWEVER, it has way, way too many ads that freeze up when loading and cras...Full ReviewThis is a very good photo editing app that is easy to use and share edited 
photos. It has a lot of functions like blemish, blur, crop, and especially 
good at drawing on the pictures to circle important items or make notes.

the app on an Android running 8.1. Wish I could pay extra to eliminate the 
ads.
